-- Baring says buys "substantial" stake in UK brand Cath Kidston
-- By Elzio Barreto
-- Tue Jul 22, 2014 04:18AM EDT
-- None



HONG KONG, July 22 (Reuters) - Baring Private Equity Asia said on Tuesday it bought a "substantial" stake in British lifestyle and fashion brand Cath Kidston for an undisclosed sum, looking to benefit from growing consumer demand for global brands in Asia.

